import React from "react"; function more(){ return (

What's More

Foot Temperature & Pressure Monitoring

Identification of high temperature & pressure zones to prevent neuropathy, foot ulcers, gangrene, etc.

Non-invasive Blood Glucose Detection

Using advanced spectroscopy we give you a range-based glucose level and detection of hyperglycemic and extreme hypoglycemic situations.

Blood Pressure Monitoring

Prevention of Systemic Hypertension through early detection of symptoms.

Emergency Detection

Sends alerts to the user's choice of contacts in the event of hypoglycemic shock, heart stroke or falls.

Algorithms that grow with you

Machine-learning based proprietary algorithms that are personally tailored according to your lifestyle and body.

Resting Heart Rate

Used to measure long term heart and kidney health and potentially prevents diabetic nephropathy and heart failure.
